    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: NHS Continuing Healthcare Checklist - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_checklist">NHS Continuing Healthcare Checklist</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_checklist">NHS Continuing Healthcare Checklist</xref>
 is used to help identify individuals who may need a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_referral_request">REFERRAL REQUEST</xref>
 for a full assessment of eligibility for 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare_checklist">NHS Continuing Healthcare Checklist</xref>, see the:        </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <div>
          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
          <p>
 part of the gov.uk website at: 
                                <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/national-framework-for-nhs-continuing-healthcare-and-nhs-funded-nursing-care" scope="external" format="html">National framework for NHS continuing healthcare and NHS-funded nursing care</xref>
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>
          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
          <p>
 website at: 
                                <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/healthcare/" scope="external" format="html">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>.                    </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
